                                                                                                                                                                                           \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n            \n    \n    \n        \n                \n                    \n                        \n                                    \u003cdiv id=\"article-body\" itemprop=\"articleBody\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA month after its announcement, we\u0026#39;re finally getting our hands on the \u003ca href=\"http://www.androidpolice.com/google-pixel-9a-announcement/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ePixel 9a\u003c/a\u003e. And for the most part, the early reviews are \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/google-pixel-9a-thoughts/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003efairly positive\u003c/a\u003e, making it a great phone to pick up if you\u0026#39;re looking for the Pixel experience on a budget. The good news is that, despite its low entry price point of $499, plenty of retailers and wireless carriers are offering discounts on the phone.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n    \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"ccf5-43a4-8f7892dd94d1\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/5-reasons-pixel-9a-android-phone-to-buy-right-now/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/google-pixel-9a-hands-on-08.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/google-pixel-9a-hands-on-08.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/google-pixel-9a-hands-on-08.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/google-pixel-9a-hands-on-08.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/google-pixel-9a-hands-on-08.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/google-pixel-9a-hands-on-08.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/google-pixel-9a-hands-on-08.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/google-pixel-9a-hands-on-08.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/google-pixel-9a-hands-on-08.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"The Pixel 9a family placed on a chess board.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/google-pixel-9a-hands-on-08.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/03/google-pixel-9a-hands-on-08.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"a-free-pixel-9a-if-you-sign-up-for-service\"\u003e\n                        A free Pixel 9a if you sign up for service\n               \u003c/h2\u003e    \n\n\u003cp\u003e The latest comes from Google Fi, offering \u003ca href=\"https://fi.google.com/about/promo-terms/?id=CdNxnLwXMQYA\u0026amp;pli=1\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003enew subscribers a Pixel 9a for free\u003c/a\u003e, so long as they sign up for a new plan and stick with the carrier for 24 months (via \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidauthority.com/google-fi-pixel-9a-free-3543685/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eAndroid Authority\u003c/a\u003e). When it comes to plans, you have a \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/best-google-fi-plans/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003evariety of different options\u003c/a\u003e, with the cheapest option starting at just $10 per month. You can also join an existing family plan in order to take advantage of this promotion. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThere\u0026#39;s also good news if you\u0026#39;re an existing Fi customer, as the carrier is also offering a separate promotion for current subscribers, knocking $200 off the Pixel 9a. Of course, you\u0026#39;ll need to have an active account with the carrier for a minimum of 120 days in order to take advantage, and make sure that any bills that come your way are paid off.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eFor the most part, that\u0026#39;s not all that bad if you\u0026#39;re already using the service. Of course, as stated before, plenty of wireless carriers are offering great deals on this phone right now, like AT\u0026amp;T offering generous payment plan options and \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/pixel-9a-is-now-available-at-att-free-pixel-buds/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ea free pair of Pixel Buds\u003c/a\u003e. \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/verizon-pixel-9a-google-premium-ai-plan-promotion/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eVerizon is giving the Pixel 9a away\u003c/a\u003e, along with a discount on Google services. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eAgain, right now is going to be the perfect time to pick up the Pixel 9a, as you\u0026#39;re going to see the best deals available during its first few weeks of release. \u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                                \n        \n                            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"76de-43ee-b55d59ce298a\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                            \n                        \t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/pixel-9a_front_porcelain-copy.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https:/